OL,3,CMinister in charge of 20mph policy
OL,4,Cconfirms he is to step down from post
OL,6,FLee Waters MS, the minister who was
OL,7,Finstrumental in implementing Wales'
OL,8,Fcontroversial 20mph policy, has
OL,9,Fconfirmed that he is to step down from
OL,10,Fhis transport position.
OL,12,FMr Waters announced on X, formerly
OL,13,Fknown as Twitter, that he will be
OL,14,Fdeleting his account when he "leaves
OL,15,Fhis transport role in a fortnight."
