OL,3,CMinister in charge of 20mph policy
OL,4,Cconfirms he is to step down from post
OL,6,FHe has been the Welsh Government's
OL,7,Fminister for climate change since
OL,8,F2021, introducing controversial
OL,9,Fpolicies including, putting a pause on
OL,10,Froad building, and the introduction of
OL,11,F20mph on many roads across the country.
OL,13,FThe move last year meant Wales became
OL,14,Fthe first UK nation to decrease the
OL,15,Fdefault speed limit to 20mph.
