OL,4,Cconfirms he is to step down from post
OL,6,FResponding to Lee Waters MS claiming
OL,7,Fhe will leave his role as Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment transport role in a
OL,9,Ffortnight, Andrew RT Davies MS, said:
OL,10,F"Motorists and business owners across
OL,11,FWales will breathe a sigh of relief at
OL,12,Fthis news.
OL,14,F"The Deputy Minister's time in post
OL,15,Fhas been characterised by one anti-
OL,16,Fmotorist policy after another, slowing
OL,17,FWales down and doing serious damage to
OL,18,Four economy.
